This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and parsing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the performance of machine learning models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with the ability of models to learn and understand language. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it discusses the performance of neural network models. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it discusses the use of a toy dataset to study the parsing ability of models.
